=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1206_1787_1653_2456.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"22%\" /></div>\n\n\n## 渑池杜氏宗谱\n\n四一四", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_1206_1787_1653_2456.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ce9674dd-366c-49ef-bdc6-726d643d12eb/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1206_1787_1653_2456.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A41%3A00Z%2F-1%2F%2Fc1a28960118233f84e43e16041a18ea5e3d132f00984e23e388503ad1fc743f1"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ce9674dd-366c-49ef-bdc6-726d643d12eb/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A41%3A01Z%2F-1%2F%2F398a06bfa9e5aea24fe07ac4a4edda4639c4dfedfe414d94e1ca69c8d93c518b", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ce9674dd-366c-49ef-bdc6-726d643d12eb/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A41%3A01Z%2F-1%2F%2F5c03dd2c615c5f1b30aeea1a1b1fcb1966b9632f0d4ad32ceabd80b5b8c934b2", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ce9674dd-366c-49ef-bdc6-726d643d12eb/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A41%3A01Z%2F-1%2F%2F022447244e3abe49fc43318f12612843bee48633b138af8d21bc7dddbdcaf1ef", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ce9674dd-366c-49ef-bdc6-726d643d12eb/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A41%3A02Z%2F-1%2F%2F1d98bd5c52062e13ea490adeb26fae2ac0b8f62c9e3b288226d95a85bc6d38a3"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ce9674dd-366c-49ef-bdc6-726d643d12eb/input_img_0.jpg